data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning two-story masterpiece boasts a classic brick exterior on three sides, giving off an air of elegance and sophistication. The interior is equally impressive, featuring a spacious layout that will instantly make you feel right at home. With an office off to the side as you walk in, which is perfectly placed behind French doors with the option for a fourth bedroom! Huge and spacious master bedroom complete with his and hers walk in closets. This sprawling space is perfect, with ample room for a king-sized bed, a cozy reading nook. You'll look forward to unwinding here after a long day, with its peaceful home-y atmosphere    This home also offers a wonderfully expansive backyard, providing you with endless opportunities for outdoor fun and relaxation. Whether you're hosting a barbecue with friends or simply enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this space will quickly become a favorite spot for you and your family.    Another major perk of this property is its prime location. You'll be within walking distance to schools, making it easy for your kids to get to class and for you to be involved in their education. Additionally, you'll be just a stone's throw away from the local splash pad and playgrounds. Perfect for summer days when you're looking for some family fun in the sun.    Overall, this home has everything you could want and more. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours - schedule a tour today and see for yourself why this property is truly extraordinary!
